Lying under oath, cutting the tags off mattresses, running with scissors, trading arms for hostages, fucking interns and/or Marilyn Monroe, spitting on the sidewalk...I don't give a shit. We have elections here, Cendan. If you don't like who wins, wait four years and try harder next time. <br>
<br>
The president is supposed to be under congressional oversight in the event of serious criminal activity...NOT congressional supervision for any reason at all. A steadily weakening executive branch is what this country cannot afford.<br>
