I am not really aware of the stereotypes of the two parties.  I forget - as a republican am I for gun control or against?  Am I for or against big programs that pay lazy people to sit home?  Feel free to fill me in on what my party stands for cause I only pick one so I can go vote on the person who I believe cares more about making change.  No, that isn't a speech or a personal attack on anyone, just my true naive stance on voting.<br>
