<br>
You can take the stance that backing out gives our country the appearance of instability but it doesn't.  When a new boss comes into the company people expect change.  Its just how it is.  Some people will lose jobs, departments will be reorganized, some people will like the new boss, and some people will miss the old boss.  <br>
